  <section class="docstring">



        <div class="specs">

            <pre translate="no"><span class="attribute">-type</span> chars_limit() :: <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:integer/0">integer</a>().</pre>

        </div>


<p>A soft limit on the number of characters returned.</p><p>When the number of characters is reached, remaining structures are
replaced by &quot;<code class="inline">...</code>&quot;. <code class="inline">CharsLimit</code> defaults to -1, which means no limit on the
number of characters returned.</p>
  </section>
</section>
